    \ingroup grp_sitemenu

    The table contains all items of site menu tree. Every menu item
    consists of:
    - unique ID;
    - name (displayed in hyperlink);
    - link (hyperlink URL);
    - ID of parent menu item (or null if it's toplevel menu item).
    - item depth inside menu three

    Recomended database schema for this table (in MySQL notation):
    \include zfb.sitemenu.sql
    
    \note All column names in this schema are hardcoded in this class
    properties and some methods of ZfBlank_SiteMenu class. Changing them
    may result in broken functionality.
    \see ZfBlank_SiteMenu
